<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Break Warning - WorkHole</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f5f5f5; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fdcb6e 0%, #e17055 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 30px; }
        .warning-box { background-color: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #fdcb6e; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
        .footer { background-color: #2c3e50; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>‚è∞ Break Almost Over!</h1>
            <p>1 minute remaining</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi <%= employee.firstName %>!</h2>
            
            <div class="warning-box">
                <h3>üö® Break Time Alert:</h3>
                <p><strong>Break Type:</strong> <%= breakType %></p>
                <p><strong>Time Remaining:</strong> 1 minute ‚è±Ô∏è</p>
                <p><strong>Started at:</strong> <%= startTime.toLocaleTimeString('en-US', { hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit', hour12: true }) %></p>
                <p><strong>Should end at:</strong> <%= new Date(startTime.getTime() + duration * 60000).toLocaleTimeString('en-US', { hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit', hour12: true }) %></p>
            </div>
            
            <p>‚ö° <strong>Time to wrap up and get ready to return to work!</strong></p>
            
            <p>Please finish your break and return to your workstation. Remember, staying on schedule helps maintain productivity for everyone! üí™</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>WorkHole - Employee Management System</p>
            <p>Helping you stay on track! ‚è∞</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>